node.text: So much of my inspiration in climbing and life has come from incredible women who came before me. Their stories of grit, passion, and creativity were a pivotal part of the paths I chose in my own life. Such stories have a ripple effect that spread throughout our society and continue to inspire future generations ✨ Proud to take part in this conversation with my biggest supporter and favorite human @adrianballinger to honor @imyourwomanmovie premiering Friday Dec. 11th on @amazonprimevideo #imyourwoman

node.title: Amazon Studios I'M YOUR WOMAN Conversation Series

node.text: Live from the home gym (the quarantine series)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ᴇᴍɪʟʏ ʜᴀʀʀɪɴɢᴛᴏɴ in Kyrgyzstan with @emilyaharrington, and @adrianballinger. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: A sign of a good trip when you already miss everyone - especially this guy, and we are only parting for a day 😂😭🥰 // thank you @adrianballinger for being the best supporter, teammate, lover, and friend through all the lows and the highs🎢 I love you so much! // #tgronlocation // 📸 @griffinkerwin

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ᴇᴍɪʟʏ ʜᴀʀʀɪɴɢᴛᴏɴ in Kyrgyzstan. May be an image of nature.

node.text: Magic all around - even in the unexpected 🇰🇬✨// #tgronlocation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ᴇᴍɪʟʏ ʜᴀʀʀɪɴɢᴛᴏɴ on August 17, 2021 tagging @emilyaharrington. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: One for the books 🇰🇬🥰 // This is 35 ✨🦙🥳 // thanks for all the bday wishes 🎉🙏🏻 // we partied hard and climbed a wall and it was the most epic all-time memorable journey ever // 📸 @adrianballinger / @austin_siadak

node.text: Mission ✅🥳 // what a journey it’s been w this one and the most special crew 🇰🇬💕 // more to come but first some more of this 💤🥰 // #tgronlocation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ᴇᴍɪʟʏ ʜᴀʀʀɪɴɢᴛᴏɴ on August 06, 2021 tagging @emilyaharrington, @kodiakcakes, and @dogcalledcat. May be an image of 1 person and dog.

node.text: V proud to be a part of the @kodiakcakes athlete team along with a bunch of rad folks ✨(& @dogcalledcat is also by association 😝) Head over to their site to check out the rest of the team (link in profile) & use the code EATLIKETHEPROS for 25% off your next order 🥞🐻💕

node.text: The expedition we need AND deserve ✨💃🏼 // we back y’all!!! // 📸 @etteloc // #tgronlocation

node.text: ‘slow is smooth, smooth is fast’ ✨lotsa switchbacks in these here mountains, but a lil zigzagging never hurt anyone….crewed up with the best in Kyrgyz 🇰🇬 and grateful for ALL the moments 🌧⚡️☀️ 💕// 📸 @austinrhopkins // #tgronlocation

Honored to have been a part of the film #WorldDebut highlighting the three new Olympic sports (🧗🏼‍♀️🏄🏽🛹✨🙌🏻) AND I got to hang w the amazing @kyra_condie during filming who will be representing the 🇺🇸 in climbing’s first ever Olympic Games 🥰💪🏼

What was once an activity practiced by a few on the outskirts of society is now making it's #worlddebut as climbing enters the Olympic arena along with skateboarding and surfing. Learn the decades long story of how these sports made it to the world stage in the latest film #worlddebut now live on @youtube. Watch now at link in bio 😬😬😬

Produced by @wzrdmedia , @boardwalkpictures. Directed by @colesax and @gknowproductions. Executive Produced by @tonyhawk. @olympics
